Bundle::Maintainer::MHASCH
==========================

Bundle for CPAN Modules maintained by Martin Becker (MHASCH).

INSTALLATION

To install this bundle type the following:

   perl -MCPAN -e "install Bundle::Maintainer::MHASCH"

